ACWA Power to Sign Agreement With Jordan Dubai Capital Tomorrow

-- B y   N a y l a   R a z z o u k
-- 
2011-06-01T15:06:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-01/acwa-power-to-sign-agreement-with-jordan-dubai-capital-tomorrow.html
ACWA Power International, a Saudi
Arabia-based company that develops electricity and water
projects, will sign a “strategic deal” tomorrow with  Jordan 
Dubai Capital on the energy sector in Jordan, the companies said
in a joint e-mailed statement.  The companies gave no further details on the agreement or
its value. A spokeswoman for Jordan Dubai Capital called by
Bloomberg declined to comment before the contracts are signed.  Jordan Dubai Capital is a Amman-based investment company
which counts among its main shareholders Dubai International
Capital LLC and Jordan’s Social Security Corp., it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Nayla Razzouk in Amman at 
 nrazzouk2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stephen Voss at 
 sev@bloomberg.net  